# Sunuwar Welfare Society System
#
# This transform for InterIndic to Sunuwar was developed for the Sunuwar Welfare Society. 
# It is primarily developed to convert Kiranti-KÃµits (Mukhia) language text from Devanagari
# to Sunuwar(KÃµits brese) script. The SWS system is intended to be the standard use of the
# Sunuwar script in both Nepal and Sikkim, India. However, at the time of preparation the Sunuwar script
# is used as an abugida in Sikkim.
#
# https://www.devkumarsunuwar.com.np/iwsadmin/imagine-filemanager/uploads/media/First%20Hamso_monthly-Magazine-Sawan-Edition_2078.pdf
# https://www.devkumarsunuwar.com.np/iwsadmin/imagine-filemanager/uploads/media/Third-Hamso-Asoj-2078-Final.pdf
#
# Originally prepared by Neil Patel <neil@jamra-patel.com>
